quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  27,77,Kandi rwose yo (Qur’an) ni umuyoboro n’impuhwe ku bemeramana
  27,78,"Mu by’ukuri Nyagasani wawe azabakiranura akoresheje itegeko rye. Kandi We ni Nyiricyubahiro bihebuje, Umumenyi uhebuje"
  27,79,Bityo (yewe Muhamadi) jya wiringira Allah! Mu by’ukuri wowe uri mu kuri kugaragara
  27,80,"Mu by’ukuri ntushobora kumvisha abapfu (ukuri), ndetse ntiwanakumvisha ibipfamatwi umuhamagaro (wawe) mu gihe bateye umugongo bagenda"
  27,81,"Kandi ntiwanashobora kuyobora impumyi (uzikura) mu buyobe bwazo, ahubwo abo wumvisha ni abemera amagambo yacu, bakaba ari na bo bicisha bugufi (Abayisilamu)"
  27,82,"N’igihe imvugo (y’ibihano) izabasohoreraho (abahakanyi), tuzabasohorera inyamaswa mu butaka ibabwira ko abantu batajyaga bizera amagambo yacu"
  27,83,"(Unibuke) umunsi tuzakoranya muri buri muryango (Umat) itsinda ry’abahakanye amagambo yacu, maze bagashyirwa ku mirongo (mu matsinda)"
  27,84,"Kugeza ubwo bazagera (imbere ya Allah) akavuga ati “Ese mwahakanye amagambo yanjye mutaranabanje kuyasobanukirwa (ngo mumenye niba ari ukuri cyangwa ari ibinyoma), cyangwa mwakoraga iki (kindi)?”"
  27,85,"Nuko imvugo (y’ibihano) ibasohoreraho kubera ibibi byabo, kandi ntibazashobora kugira icyo bavuga (biregura)"
  27,86,"Ese ntibabona ko twabashyiriyeho ijoro kugira ngo bariruhukemo, n’amanywa kugira ngo babashe kubona (bityo bashake ibibabeshaho)? Mu by’ukuri muri ibyo harimo ibimenyetso ku bantu bemera"
  27,87,"(Unibuke) umunsi impanda izavuzwa, maze ibiri mu birere no mu isi bigakangarana, uretse uwo Allah azashaka (guhumuriza). Kandi bose bazamugana bicishije bugufi"
  27,88,"Uzanabona imisozi wibwire ko iri hamwe, nyamara izaba igenda yihuta nk’ibicu. Ibyo ni ibikorwa na Allah, We watunganyije buri kintu. Mu by’ukuri We azi byimazeyo ibyo mukora"